## Profiling

Built-in profiling for CPU (pyinstrument), memory (tracemalloc), SQL queries, and frontend
Web Vitals. See [docs/PROFILING.md](docs/PROFILING.md) for full usage guide.

```bash
task backend:profile:cpu       # CPU flame chart
task backend:profile:memory    # Memory snapshot
task backend:profile:report    # Open latest HTML report
```

